{"tid":2309372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本立法規定國民有義務接種疫苗 政府負擔全部費用","createTime":"2020-12-02T13:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:09:47.000Z","uid":174246,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9ca33d25cf0e293d96e4e0412abaef156d7f00","tid":2309372,"uid":174246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:23:15.000Z","msg":"CLS政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本參議院12月2日一致通過一項草案，修訂《預防接種法》，規定國民有義務接種武肺疫苗。<br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）2日報道，地方政府會負責執行疫苗接種的工作。中央政府則會支付接種疫苗的全部費用。如果民眾接種疫苗後引起健康問題，政府會支付醫療費用。若藥廠需要向接種疫苗後出現健康問題的民眾支付費用，政府也會賠償藥廠的損失。"},{"pid":"378b70fc4d3d1783a35f5d606cb39c7ca379005d","tid":2309372,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"唔想打都迫人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9826e26d3490ee7d2d5079f14a74f5e8c384395","tid":2309372,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"無野呀嘛日本政府"},{"pid":"a6266df5d805afd95b3d8d653f7c7d2b9f6332fb","tid":2309372,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:28:02.000Z","msg":"唉！對日本政府失望，迫人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03ae47148acbe8057759855c33a7058c0bd6599","tid":2309372,"uid":132446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"問題賠幾多先?"},{"pid":"48c82735a3aa523054d99c8f966b4bda654ef0ad","tid":2309372,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:28:46.000Z","msg":"deep state藥廠fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322f9d38cfa3046368eb367f6c35693a0b594cc3","tid":2309372,"uid":64636,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"日本個疫苗